      "text": "LocatedatDisney's Blizzard Beach Water Park"
    },
    {
      "line": 4,
      "text": "You’ll have it made in the shade with this convenient upgrade that includes beach umbrellas, seating and more."
    },
    {
      "line": 5,
      "text": "All Ages"
    },
    {
